    "finding": "inverse SELECTION generalizes -- it beats the no-oracle null broadly. The LEARNED oracle earning its keep over BLOSUM62 does NOT. The blaTEM PASS is not representative: on most proteins a 1992 substitution matrix proposes edits as well as ESM2-650M does.",
